7e86&d_curPage=5&d_pageSize=40&d_headId=a5e9508985e308900fd4e24e902f7e86&d_posi=15&skId=cjuipswizvn58hxyk4wt3eroj2nvtbp9&fkId=cjuipswizvn58hxyk4wt3eroj2nvtbp9&ckId=58zxelsqynlss0ksr33bpkki6b99dz48&sfrom=search_job_pc&curPage=5&pageSize=40&index=15','机器学习','上海',30000,13000,21500,'概述\n客户经理将管理工作轨道，并作为 AI 解决方案组内的战略客户合作伙伴。Dataforce 是一个快速发展的新部门，为世界上一些最负盛名的科技公司提供高质量的人机交互数据。我们部门专注于收集、丰富和处理不同人工智能领域的机器学习训练数据。理想的候选人将具有 B2B 销售经验，以及与战略分析和营销相关的技能。您将负责识别潜在客户并发展客户关系。\n\n成功的客户经理将具备扎实的销售和客户管理能力以及解决问题的能力，以及与多个地区的客户和内部团队建立牢固关系的能力。\n\n描述\n识别目标市场中的潜在客户，并对潜在客户的业务和技术需求进行适当的研究\n与售前和生产团队合作，为当前和潜在客户制定赢得合同的提案\n识别、限定和量化机会\n从潜在客户产生一直到关闭的过程中推动机会\n确保客户成功和满意度\n起草和实施商业计划\n了解客户的业务和技术要求\n成为我们业务产品、流程和运营方面的主题专家，并及时了解行业新闻\n在 TransPerfect 的 CRM 系统上跟踪商机\n协调不同时区和文化的生产和技术团队\n产生和管理高价值的盈利业务交易\n 识别、跟踪和管理 KPI，并提供内部和面向客户的状态报告；提供执行更新，包括帐户进度、健康状况、风险和机会\n 参加展会并通过参与案例研究和社交媒体来支持营销工作\n提供准确的每周预测\n协助制定总体计划/预算并随后遵守；掌握指定客户业务的整体财务状况；提高流程、人员和技术的效率\n管理围绕自有业务和帐户的利益相关者沟通\n协助内部和客户团队培训和采用技术和服务\n提出并实施新的创新产品\n\n所需技能\n在定义项目物流、资源和生产流程方面拥有成熟的经验\n出色的计划、组织和沟通能力\n优秀的英语书面和口头沟通能力\n独立，自我激励，以结果为导向，充满活力\n能够在紧迫的期限内与地理位置分散的团队合作\n优秀的人际交往和谈判技巧\n 项目管理和报告工具的高级知识\n所需的经验和资格\n工商管理，计算机科学，人工智能或相关领域的最低学士学位，\n有管理复杂项目的经验，\n管理不同地域团队的领导经验，\n在客户咨询、解决方案设计和销售方法方面的经验，\n熟练使用 Microsoft Office 应用程序，包括 Outlook、Word、Excel 和 PowerPoint 以及行业特定的分析软件，\n对行业有基本的了解，有能力成为工作中的主题专家，\n创新和解决问题的能力，包括为我们的客户开发和提出专家数据解决方案的能力，\n强大的分析和解决问题的能力，具有在压力下工作和按时交付的能力\n\n所需的技能和经验\n在人工智能行业的先前经验\n具有多任务和组织行政工作的能力\n 机器智能、人工智能、项目管理或相关学科的学位\n熟练掌握一门外语\n具有强大的咨询背景是首选，但不是要求\n高级商业学位\n\n\n\n\nOVERVIEW\nThe Account Manager will manage tracks of work and act as a strategic customer partner within the AI Solutions group. Dataforce is a new, rapidly growing division offering high quality data for Human Machine Interaction to some of the most prestigious technology companies in the world. Our department focuses on gathering, enriching and processing training data for Machine Learning in different AI domains. The ideal candidate will have experience in B2B sales, as well as skills related to strategic analysis and marketing. You will be responsible for identifying leads and developing client relationships.\n\nA successful Account Manager will have solid sales & client management and problem solving skills, and the ability to build strong relationships with client and internal teams in multiple geographies.\n\nDESCRIPTION\nIdentify potential clients in the target market and complete appropriate research on the prospective client’s business and technical needs\nPartner with pre-sales and production teams to create contract-winning proposals for current and prospective clients\nIdentify, qualify and quantify opportunities\nDrive opportunities from lead generation all the way to closure\nEnsure customer success and satisfaction\nDraft and implement business plans\nUnderstand client’s business and technical requirements\nBecome a subject matter expert on our business products, processes and operations, and remain up to date on industry news\nKeep track of business opportunities on TransPerfect’s CRM system\nCoordinate production and technology teams across different time zones and cultures\nGenerate and manage high-value profitable business deals\nIdentify, track and manage KPIs and provide internal and client facing status reports; providing of executive updates including account progress, health, risk and opportunities\nAttend tradeshows and support marketing efforts by contributing to case studies and social media\nProvide accurate weekly forecasts\nAssist in building overall plans/budgets and subsequent adherence; own the overall financial health of assigned client engagements; drive efficiencies across process, people and technology\nManage stakeholder communication around owned business and accounts\nAssist in training and adoption of technologies and services for internal and client teams\nPropose and implement new innovative offerings\n\nREQUIRED SKILLS\nProven experience defining project logistics, resources, and production processes \nExcellent planning, organizational, and communication skills\nExcellent written and verbal communication skills in English\nIndependent, self-motivated, results-oriented, and dynamic\nAbility to work under tight deadlines and with geographically dispersed teams\nExcellent interpersonal and negotiation skills\nAdvanced knowledge of project management and reporting tools\nREQUIRED EXPERIENCE AND QUALIFICATIONS\nMinimum Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration, Computer Science, Artificial Intelligence or related fields,\nPrior experience in managing complex projects,\nLeadership experience in managing diverse geographical teams,\nPrior experience in client consulting, solutions design, and sales methodologies,\nProficiency in Microsoft Office applications, including Outlook, Word, Excel and PowerPoint and industry-specific analysis software,\nBasic understanding of the industry, with the ability to become a subject matter expert on the job,\nInnovation and problem-solving skills that include the ability to develop and propose expert data solutions for our clients,\nStrong analytical and problem-solving skills, with proven ability to work under pressure and delivery against deadlines\n\nDESIRED SKILLS AND EXPERIENCE\nPrior experience in the Artificial Intelligence industry\nAbility for multitask and organize administrative work\nDegree in Machine Intelligence, Artificial Intelligence, Project Management, or related discipline\nProficiency in a foreign language\nA strong consulting background is preferred but not a requirement\nAdvanced business degree'),(595,'3D & UX设计师-SeedV实验室-人工智能工程院','15-30k·13薪','创新工场(北京)企业管理股份有限公司','北京-海淀区','https://www.liepin.com/job/1950825991.shtml?d_sfrom=search_prime&d_ckId=a5e9508985e308900fd4e24e902f7e86&d_curPage=5&d_pageSize=40&d_headId=a5e9508985e308900fd4e24e902f7e86&d_posi=16&skId=cjuipswizvn58hxyk4wt3eroj2nvtbp9&fkId=cjuipswizvn58hxyk4wt3eroj2nvtbp9&ckId=58zxelsqynlss0ksr33bpkki6b99dz