nical teams\nDegree in Computer Science, Mathematics or related field\nProficiency in:\nJava & Spring\nREST APIs\nGit, Maven\nExpertise building large scale web applications\nExperience working with Microservices, Event Driven and Domain Driver Design architecture patterns\nExpertise in Application Lifecycle Management using a tool such as Jenkins, Bamboo or Shippable\nKnowledge of using relational databases and non-relational databases\nAbility to communicate clearly technical designs and objectives\nProfessional proficiency in English\nKnowledge of Agile and Scrum methodologies\n\nIt’s A Bonus If You Have\nExperience with Docker containerization and Kubernetes orchestration\nExperience in Frontend development building responsive UIs using JS Frameworks such as React\nExperience of TDD, BDD and Automated Testing Practices\nExpertise in DevOps and Continuous Delivery / Deployment\n'),(972,'高级 Java 研发工程师-智能方向','20-40k·15薪','滴滴','北京-海淀区','https://www.liepin.com/job/1951226385.shtml?d_sfrom=search_prime&d_ckId=1bc4c8fc18607ce1d9f3bccaf7469bbd&d_curPage=5&d_pageSize=40&d_headId=1bc4c8fc18607ce1d9f3bccaf7469bbd&d_posi=11&skId=dvsty8de5kjof0otxj7q5kurags77j78&fkId=dvsty8de5kjof0otxj7q5kurags77j78&ckId=wovlneqeq8mg0lzcyo94kc2fgqpua608&sfrom=search_job_pc&curPage=5&pageSize=40&index=11','java','北京',40000,20000,30000,'岗位职责：\n1. 参与滴滴智能机器人平台、语音客服平台、智能分析平台的工程开发工作；\n2. 参与到滴滴客服智能化转型核心战役中，用技术手段解决业务和用户问题；\n3. 独当一面与产品、运营、数据团队完成需求对接、系统分析、设计和编码任务，保证交付进度和质量；\n4. 承担项目中核心模块的设计开发与优化，保障系统迭代效率和可用性；\n5. 有机会参与智能知识库的开源工作，回馈技术社区。\n\n任职资格：\n1. 计算机相关专业，本科及以上学历，3 年以上服务端开发经验；\n2. Java 编码能力过硬，熟练掌握常用数据结构和算法，熟悉Spring生态的框架工具；\n4. 思维活跃，学习能力强，有一定的抗压能力，善于沟通和团队协作，乐于分享；\n5. 有IVR、智能机器人、智能知识库等经验更好；\n6. 有参与开源项目的经验或熟悉开源工程运作更好。'),(973,'java高级工程师','25-35k·16薪','国泰君安','上海-浦东新区','https://www.liepin.com/job/1947311747.shtml?d_sfrom=search_prime&d_ckId=1bc4c8fc18607ce1d9f3bccaf7469bbd&d_curPage=5&d_pageSize=40&d_headId=1bc4c8fc18607ce1d9f3bccaf7469bbd&d_posi=12&skId=dvsty8de5kjof0otxj7q5kurags77j78&fk